      "updated": 1672750926
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d439f",
      "text": "from [/villagepump/瞑想で目を閉じる必要はない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a0",
      "text": "from [独断的瞑想解説]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a1",
      "text": "瞑想で目を閉じる必要はない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a2",
      "text": "Q: 目を閉じますか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a3",
      "text": "　A: 基本閉じないですね[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a4",
      "text": "　　仏教方面で名前がついてたはず",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a5",
      "text": "　　　「[半眼]」か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a6",
      "text": "　　　>仏像の眼（まなこ）は、見開くでもなく閉じてもいない、いわゆる「半眼」の眼差しです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a7",
      "text": "　　　https://mjj.or.jp/message/第66回%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C半眼の眼差し%E3%80%8D",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a8",
      "text": "　　歩く時に目を閉じたら危ない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43a9",
      "text": "　　　今気づいたけども、今の僕にとって散歩が瞑想の位置を占めてるんだなぁ[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43aa",
      "text": "　　[蝋燭]とか[焚き火]とかを見つめるやり方もよくある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43ab",
      "text": "　　　[一点注視法]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43ac",
      "text": "　　　[護摩]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43ad",
      "text": "　　　[トラタカ瞑想]って言葉もあるみたいね、今知った",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43ae",
      "text": "　　「閉じてはいけない」ってわけでもないのでどっちでも好きにしたらいいと思いますけど「閉じるべきだ」という主張には根拠がない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
    {
      "id": "63b4274baff09e00004d43af",
      "text": "　　　閉じなくても感情が揺さぶられないような環境に行くことがまず優先",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672750924,
      "updated": 1672750924
    },
